{"tid":50330,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"［LIHKG] 廢柴 企吧！！關愛一生 試唱","createTime":"2016-12-22T10:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-07T23:32:59.000Z","uid":4353,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45e6ecc9d629ac238c5e069d828879a93f22aa92","tid":50330,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"原歌詞由：<br />\n矛盾只因關愛座<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/29045/page/9?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/29045/page/9?ref=ios</a><br />\n裡面嘅所以巴絲所提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次唱，屋企冇任何PRO錄音儀器，所以電腦播音樂用電話錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n音樂用YOUTUBE人地彈嘅:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIVcHbCR4xk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvIVcHbCR4xk&d=BQFZMQbI4Ti67tyD06YAmEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=69be96c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIVcHbCR4xk</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時只係唱左半首，希望企緊地鐵火車巴士的士嘅你慢慢收聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收聽請移玉步去：<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-465340638/05-sugarpova/s-eo9EA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-465340638%2F05-sugarpova%2Fs-eo9EA&d=BQFZMQbI4Ti67tyD06YAmEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b829d040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-465340638/05-sugarpova/s-eo9EA</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n關愛一生<br />\n<br />\n返左一天fullday過後想坐下<br />\n只想抖返一下 就坐下<br />\n心中忐忑過後還是 企出去<br />\n卻發覺經已被人 捕進鏡裏<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因關愛座 坐得嗎<br />\n常期望有空位坐剩 然後抖下<br />\n你問我做乜唔恰下 怕被人睥嘛<br />\n坐就批鬥 廢柴 企吧<br />\n回頭看咁多關愛座 你SIT嗎<br />\n竟會沒呀嬸埋位<br />\n當佢仍然未想坐<br />\n就讓我先坐吧<br />\n這個決定多麼錯"},{"pid":"74cf205d53273770feadf5dc82ebe3508463dbc3","tid":50330,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"絲打唱得都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185ebff6078ae1daf2faad68b81e5adbd4729d05","tid":50330,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打唱得都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e177d1600764e8a18a64f7d2ea43126722a30f0e","tid":50330,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f5accc9d671bb04a96565bca42e9e4eedeacb1","tid":50330,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e75e15687555f3c2d48d2d31f2d43676b5e4b74","tid":50330,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca9127aee547eed3f48e5ebfdc5c33ec00af01b","tid":50330,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" cla